{"data":{"markdownRemark":null,"npmPackage":{"name":"gatsby-source-unsplash","description":"Source plugin for Gatsby to pull in unsplash photos using their API","keywords":["Gatsby","Unsplash","gatsby-plugin"],"lastPublisher":{"name":"vacas5","avatar":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/ce51967b337807e35940d46d1cf03cdb"},"repository":{"url":"https://github.com/vacas5/gatsby-source-unsplash"},"readme":{"childMarkdownRemark":{"html":"<h1 id=\"gatsby-source-unsplash\"><a href=\"#gatsby-source-unsplash\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>gatsby-source-unsplash</h1>\n<p>Source plugin for pulling photo data by collection into Gatsby from the official <a href=\"https://unsplash.com/developers\">Unsplash API</a>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"install\"><a href=\"#install\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Install</h2>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">npm install --save gatsby-source-unsplash</code></p>\n<h2 id=\"how-to-use\"><a href=\"#how-to-use\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>How to use</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\">\n      <pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// In your gatsby-config.js</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Application id provided by Unsplash</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Collections must be public to return photos</span>\nplugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    resolve<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`gatsby-source-unsplash`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    options<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      appId<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`12345678`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      collections<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n        <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`098765`</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token comment\">// optional: will only get page 1, so increase this count to include > 10 photos</span>\n      perPage<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`100`</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre>\n      </div>\n<h2 id=\"how-to-query\"><a href=\"#how-to-query\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>How to query</h2>\n<p>Get all photo urls in reverse chronological order with the photographer’s name:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"graphql\">\n      <pre class=\"language-graphql\"><code class=\"language-graphql\"><span class=\"token keyword\">query</span> PhotosQuery <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    allUnsplashPhoto<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token attr-name\">sort</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">fields</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>created_at<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">order</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> DESC <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      edges <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        node <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n          id\n          user <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n            id\n            name\n          <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n          urls <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n            full\n            regular\n            small\n          <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n          description\n          created_at\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre>\n      </div>\n<p>Get a specific photo’s urls by id with links to photographer’s Unsplash profile:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"graphql\">\n      <pre class=\"language-graphql\"><code class=\"language-graphql\"><span class=\"token keyword\">query</span> PhotoQuery <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    unsplashPhoto<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">eq</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"GnY_mW1Q6Xc\"</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        id\n        description\n        urls <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n            full\n            regular\n            small\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        user <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n            name\n            links <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n                html\n            <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre>\n      </div>","timeToRead":1}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/packages/gatsby-source-unsplash/","id":"f23af0af-08fd-59cd-9426-7f4160d651c9"}}